[FILE:429:descriptions/desc.single]
Tidy is a console application for Mac OS X, Linux, Windows, UNIX, and 
more.  It corrects and cleans up HTML and XML documents by fixing markup
errors and upgrading legacy code to modern standards.

libtidy is a C static and dynamic library that developers can integrate
into their applications in order to bring all of Tidy???s power to your
favorite tools. libtidy is used today in desktop applications, web
servers, and more.


